data.name: label12.Text
data.value: Message of the Day (MOTD). Displayed below the tile image and above the username/password fields. Valid substitutions: %m - Machine name, %d - Today's date, %i - IP address, %n - DNS name, %v pGina version

data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: WARNING: Disabling a credential provider can be risky. If pGina malfunctions or otherwise prevents access to the machine, it may be necessary to boot into safe mode in order to restore access. Before disabling a credential provider, be sure you know what you're doing. You have been warned.
